                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Terres</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Port au Prince</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1902-11-05">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 5, 1902</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Terres reports that Gonaives political refugees are claimed by General Nord;
                    that consul has been instructed not to deliver them, and that Livingston has
                    been instructed to advise the U. S. S. <hi rend="italic">Cincinnati.</hi>)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
